rawResponse:
## Solution

```css
.container {
  width: 98%; /* 1200px/100% */
  margin: 0 auto;

  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .card {
    width: calc(50vw - 40px); /* 300px/1200px*50% */

    margin: 10px auto;
  }

  .container {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
```

